    <narrative xml:lang="EN">3. To create a safe, protective and inclusive environment for children in their community</narrative>
   </title>
   <reference code="265636" vocabulary="99"></reference>
   <indicator aggregation-status="0" ascending="0" measure="1">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Assessment of results: The parents have played a very important role in family parenting and their contribution has made the community more harmonious. The project team developed six sessions on positive parenting training, including how to encourage children to cooperate with adults, the methods instead of punishment, to teach children how to be independent etc. The sessions have been very useful for parents who know very little about positive parenting. The parent gained a sound understanding of education notions, and their educational and parenting behaviours have been improved to some extent. Parent-children relationships have improved and many parents have achieved personal development in the project.</narrative>
